Introduction

Today I would like to introduce a virtual currency to people. Virtual currency is any currency that is not printed on paper or printed on metal, so it is virtual and exists only in the virtual world. With the development of the times, more and more virtual currencies are appearing in our life. For this reason, people also have electronic wallets. What is staored on such wallets are not dollars or euros but virtual currencies (Bitcoin, Ethereum...)
